window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The epic conclusion to the LitRPG series Master Hunter K.</b></p> <p>The circus of death to prove the worth of mankind is reaching its bloody finale.</p> <p>Fighting the monsters threatening to overwhelm mankind brought out the best and the worst out of humanity. And true to its purpose as a measurement of worthiness, ultimate victory in the raids would require more than just strength. The final chapter awaits, the judgment of the fate of mankind is about to begin.</p> <p><i>Translated by Oppatranslations.</i></p>"; 
